===Etymology===
Uncertain. Two theories are prominent: a relation to the Germanic {{w|Silingi}} tribe, whose name derives from [[Ancient Greek]] {{m|grc|Σιλίγγαι}} of uncertain further origin, or from [[Old Slavic]] [[ślęg]]/[[śląg]].

